    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_12478_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/12478/4750_12478_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "When, therefore, they had come to this resolution, as being best for them, they went against their enemies; but those enemies were not dismayed either at the attack itself, or at the great multitude that made it, and received them with great courage.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_12478_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/12478/4750_12478_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "Many of the hebrews were slain; and the remainder of the army, upon the disorder of their troops, were pursued, and fled, after a shameful manner, to their camp. Whereupon this unexpected misfortune made them quite despond; and they hoped for nothing that was good; as gathering from it, that this affliction came from the wrath of God, because they rashly went out to war without his approbation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_12478_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/12478/4750_12478_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "The Sedition Of Corah And Of The Multitude Against Moses, And Against His Brother, Concerning The Priesthood.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_12478_000009_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/12478/4750_12478_000009_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "So I will first explain the cause whence this sedition arose, and then will give an account of the sedition itself; as also of what settlements made for their government after it was over.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_12478_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/12478/4750_12478_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "So that it was not a thing that I pretend to give, but only according to the determination of God; I therefore propose it still to be contended for by such as please to put in for it, only desiring that he who has been already preferred, and has already obtained it, may be allowed now also to offer himself for a candidate.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_12478_000012_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/12478/4750_12478_000012_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "However, he himself will judge again who it shall be whom he would have to offer sacrifices to him, and to have the direction of matters of religion; for it is absurd that Corah, who is ambitious of this honor, should deprive God of the power of giving it to whom he pleases.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_12478_000012_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/12478/4750_12478_000012_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "Do thou also come, that this contest about this honorable employment may receive determination.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "six.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "CHAPTER seven.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "And when he had joined battle with the enemy, he beat them; and pursuing them as they fled, he destroyed them all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000003_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000003_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "Some they starved out with famine, and some they gained by other methods; and after all, he betook himself to slay the women and the children, and thought he did not act therein either barbarously or inhumanly; first, because they were enemies whom he thus treated, and, in the next place, because it was done by the command of God, whom it was dangerous not to obey.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000003_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000003_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "He also took Agag, the enemies' king, captive,--the beauty and tallness of whose body he admired so much, that he thought him worthy of preservation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000003_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000003_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "The multitude were also guilty, together with Saul; for they spared the herds and the flocks, and took them for a prey, when God had commanded they should not spare them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "Hereupon Saul returned home with joy, for the glorious things he had done, and for the conquest of his enemies, as though he had not neglected any thing which the prophet had enjoined him to do when he was going to make war with the Amalekites, and as though he had exactly observed all that he ought to have done.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "As soon therefore as God had rejected the intercession of the prophet, and it plainly appeared he would not change his mind, at break of day Samuel came to Saul at Gilgal.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000005_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000005_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "Wherefore take notice, that thou art under the wrath of God, for thou hast despised and neglected what he commanded thee.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000005_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000005_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "unless perhaps thou dost imagine that it is almost all one to offer it in sacrifice to God as to destroy it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000005_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000005_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "\"But forgive me,\" said he, \"and be merciful to me, for I will be cautious how I offend for the time to come.\" He also entreated the prophet to go back with him, that he might offer his thank offerings to God; but Samuel went home, because he saw that God would not be reconciled to him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "Hereupon Saul said that he had been wicked, but that what was done could not be undone: he therefore desired him to honor him so far, that the multitude might see that he would accompany him in worshipping God.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "So Samuel granted him that favor, and went with him and worshipped God.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000006_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000006_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "Agag also, the king of the Amalekites, was brought to him; and when the king asked, How bitter death was?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "CHAPTER eight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "How, Upon Saul's Transgression Of The Prophet's Commands, Samuel Ordained Another Person To Be King Privately, Whose Name Was David, As God Commanded Him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "Now Saul being sensible of the miserable condition he had brought himself into, and that he had made God to be his enemy, he went up to his royal palace at Gibeah, which name denotes a hill, and after that day he came no more into the presence of the prophet.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "But Samuel said, he was afraid lest Saul, when he came to know of it, should kill him, either by some private method or even openly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000008_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000008_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "But he was mistaken in judging about God's providence; for when Samuel inquired of God whether he should anoint this youth, whom he so admired, and esteemed worthy of the kingdom, God said, \"Men do not see as God seeth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000008_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000008_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "And when the prophet saw that these were no way inferior to the eldest in their countenances, he inquired of God which of them it was whom he chose for their king.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000008_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000008_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "And when God said it was none of them, he asked Jesse whether he had not some other sons besides these; and when he said that he had one more, named David, but that he was a shepherd, and took care of the flocks, Samuel bade them call him immediately, for that till he was come they could not possibly sit down to the feast.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000008_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000008_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "Now, as soon as his father had sent for David, and he was come, he appeared to be of a yellow complexion, of a sharp sight, and a comely person in other respects also.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000008_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000008_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "This is he, said Samuel privately to himself, whom it pleases God to make our king.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "But the Divine Power departed from Saul, and removed to David; who, upon this removal of the Divine Spirit to him, began to prophesy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26486_000009_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26486/4750_26486_000009_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
        "content": "So Jesse sent his son, and gave him presents to carry to Saul.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4750_26487_000000_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4750/26487/4750_26487_000000_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4750",
